Class CLCodeAttribute

  • java.lang.Object
    • jminusminus.CLAttributeInfo
      • jminusminus.CLCodeAttribute
  • class CLCodeAttribute
extends CLAttributeInfo
    Representation of Code_attribute structure (JVM Spec Section 4.8.2). This is a required method attribute.
